$$
A =
\begin{bmatrix}
12 & -51 & 4\\
6 & 167 & -68\\
-4 & 24 & -41
\end{bmatrix}
$$

Multiply by the householder matrix
$$
H = I - \beta vv^T
$$
$$
(I - \beta (a-\|a\|e_1)(a-\|a\|e_1)^T) a
=
a - \beta (a - \|a\|e_1)(a^T a - \|a\|e_1^T a)
$$
For
$$
\beta (a^T a - \|a\| (e_1^T a)) = 1
$$

$a$ is a vector
$u = a - \|a\|e$
$$
u^T*u
=
(a^T-\|a\|e^T)(a-\|a\|e)
=
2\|a\|^2 - 2\|a\|(e^T a)
$$

$$
u^T a = (a-\|a\|e)^T(a)
=
\|a\|^2 - \|a\|(e^Ta)
$$
$$
u^Ta / u^Tu
=
(\|a\|^2 - \|a\|(e^Ta))/(2\|a\|^2 - 2\|a\|(e^T a))
= 1/2
$$
$$
uu^Ta/u^Tu
=
(1/2) (a - \|a\|e)
$$
